* Facilities and Maintenance, providing carpentry, electrical equipment and air conditioning services, and plumbing;
* Road and equipment maintenance;
* Water and Sewerage supplies and maintenance;
* Solid Waste management;
* Other miscellaneous services including design and engineering and unexploded ordinance controls.
